HEADWORD: Erythrochroism
<hw>E*ryth"ro*chro*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>'eryqro`s</grk> red + <?/ color.]</ety> <fld>(Zo⟦oum⟧l.)</fld>
